                lo antes posible</p>
            <div>
                <label for="message" class="block mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Email*</label>
                <input type="text"
                    class="block p-2.5 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300">
            </div>
            <div>
